Summary: Saw gray-silver claw over my house.
divs: sighting detailsi was taking the garbage out with my dog. i stopped and looked up at the stars. this morning it was clear and beautiful and a lot of stars. as i was looking up i saw a shooting star going east to west. i was facing east. then this strange object came into view. this was gray-silver claw i saw it 3 seconds then it dematerialized at the same time it was going south to north. it showed itself than cloaked invisable. that is incredible to do. the claw was 5 ft then rapidly gone, (wit's name and town deleted--sgonzalez\cms).
